1
00:01:40,600 --> 00:01:44,039
A great fire destroyed the Qin family.

2
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,600
But fortunately,

3
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,930
there was a hidden hut outside the courtyard.

4
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:53,080
It was filled with my father

5
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:57,200
and grandfather's years of autopsy and case

6
00:01:57,520 --> 00:01:59,120
files and notes.

7
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:01,080
Under the moonlight,

8
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:03,360
I moved them all back to my pharmacy.

9
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,760
When I was twelve,

10
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:07,840
the landlord took back the deed.

11
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,280
Luckily, Chunyi took me in,

12
00:02:10,919 --> 00:02:12,920
so I had a place to settle down again.

13
00:02:13,120 --> 00:02:14,120
Since then,

14
00:02:14,680 --> 00:02:16,880
I read all kinds of case files every day,

15
00:02:17,160 --> 00:02:20,320
hoping to find the murderer who killed my family one day.

16
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:25,920
You are actually still alive.

17
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:31,040
Why didn't you come to me?

18
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,240
I am sorry,

19
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:40,640
Uncle Su.

20
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,840
Because on that day,

21
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:49,120
a silenced murderer

22
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,730
said to another person next to him,

23
00:02:52,040 --> 00:02:53,200
"Your Honor."

24
00:02:54,079 --> 00:02:55,480
I knew then

25
00:02:55,760 --> 00:02:58,890
that a high-ranking court official wiped out my family.

26
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:02,600
His minions and spies

27
00:03:02,840 --> 00:03:04,480
must be all around.

28
00:03:05,920 --> 00:03:08,560
Knowing the person but not their deeds,

29
00:03:09,640 --> 00:03:11,640
their identities are hard to guess.

30
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:14,160
Even though we have met now,

31
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:17,100
I didn't dare to acknowledge you.

32
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,600
But fortunately,

33
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:26,740
since the truth of Su Xiang's case was revealed,

34
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,079
I am certain

35
00:03:30,000 --> 00:03:32,460
that your friendship with my father is deep.

36
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:43,440
Didn't you also say

37
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:47,380
that my eyes and brows look a bit like his?

38
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,320
Great.

39
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,200
Great.

40
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:06,680
So Constable Qin has descendants.

41
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:10,480
The Qin family still has descendants.

42
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,640
But for this case,

43
00:04:18,600 --> 00:04:20,839
I must get to the bottom of it

44
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:23,000
and bring the murderer to justice.

45
00:04:23,840 --> 00:04:27,570
Only then can I console all those in my Qin family who died unjustly.

46
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,480
But now you are in prison,

47
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:33,060
how will you investigate?

48
00:04:34,200 --> 00:04:35,730
I went to prison on purpose.

49
00:04:38,720 --> 00:04:41,380
You actually could have proven your innocence.

50
00:04:41,840 --> 00:04:44,040
But you realized you were being watched,

51
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:46,560
so you thought the prison was the safest place.

52
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,600
Exactly.

53
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:51,840
The wound on the victim's chest was about 1.3 inches deep.

54
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:55,440
Normally, the blood would have sprayed out.

55
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,880
But strangely,

56
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,400
the front of my clothes was completely clean,

57
00:04:59,400 --> 00:05:01,130
without a single drop of blood.

58
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:04,680
Instead, my back was covered in mottled bloodstains.

59
00:05:04,880 --> 00:05:06,280
This shows that at the time of the crime,

60
00:05:06,280 --> 00:05:08,520
after the real killer ambushed and knocked me down,

61
00:05:08,520 --> 00:05:10,680
when he pulled the knife from the victim's chest,

62
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:11,960
the gushing blood

63
00:05:12,160 --> 00:05:14,240
splashed onto my back as I lay face down.

64
00:05:14,240 --> 00:05:14,960
Then,

65
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:18,080
the real killer shoved the murder weapon into my hand.

66
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:21,160
But the flaws in the distribution of bloodstains on the clothes

67
00:05:21,160 --> 00:05:23,820
are exactly the key to breaking the conspiracy.

68
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,480
If the death of Constable Qin

69
00:05:26,720 --> 00:05:30,320
is because he found out the truth of the colored glaze pearl case,

70
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:33,240
then the mastermind behind the scenes

71
00:05:33,840 --> 00:05:37,159
must be the Minister of Works, Yuan Feng.

72
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:39,560
If you want to know the inside story,

73
00:05:39,560 --> 00:05:42,020
you can ask Lu Yunxian who was just released.

74
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,280
Although Lu Yunxian has been released,

75
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:47,010
he is actually less safe now than he was in prison.

76
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:49,200
If we want to investigate the case,

77
00:05:49,200 --> 00:05:51,130
I'm afraid we don't have much time.

78
00:05:54,760 --> 00:05:55,760
Vice Governor Li.

79
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,370
You are the only one who can help me now.

80
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:14,400
Just pretend I'm not here.

81
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,480
Father, I understand.

82
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:18,170
I'll go with you.

83
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:21,620
Jueming will face many dangers on this trip.

84
00:06:21,640 --> 00:06:22,640
I will go with him,

85
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:24,160
so I can keep him safe.

86
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,320
After finding out the truth,

87
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,960
I will come back.

88
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:38,080
I heard nothing.

89
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,560
Mr. Lu,

90
00:06:57,159 --> 00:06:59,240
Squire Lu was murdered.

91
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:00,740
He broke out of prison.

92
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:08,480
A wet-behind-the-ears kid

93
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,440
dares to play tricks on me, huh?

94
00:07:11,080 --> 00:07:12,120
Very well.

95
00:07:12,240 --> 00:07:14,040
Then I'll play along with him.

96
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:16,040
Get up.

97
00:07:20,040 --> 00:07:23,170
It was inconvenient to make a move while he was in prison.

98
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,560
Now that he's out,

99
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,420
it's not up to him anymore.

100
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,320
Yun'er.

101
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:37,240
I never thought you would

102
00:07:39,159 --> 00:07:43,120
give your life to save me.

103
00:07:43,480 --> 00:07:44,320
Minister Lu,

104
00:07:45,280 --> 00:07:48,920
what is the hidden truth behind the collapse of the Anlan Dam?

105
00:07:49,640 --> 00:07:52,080
Too many people lost their lives because of it.

106
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,610
Please tell me everything.

107
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:02,880
When the Anlan Dam collapsed,

108
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,920
the Emperor was furious.

109
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:10,680
Yuan Feng, the Minister of Works, pretended to conduct a thorough investigation.

110
00:08:11,120 --> 00:08:14,560
In the end, he brought in two scapegoats.

111
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:18,160
He stated directly

112
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:22,800
that Cui Yide, the Water Conservancy Director of the Ministry of Works,

113
00:08:22,800 --> 00:08:27,000
colluded with the Anlan Dam designer, Ye Hongru,

114
00:08:27,880 --> 00:08:33,559
to alter the dam's dimensions and materials,

115
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:36,440
and embezzled the funds.

116
00:08:38,240 --> 00:08:39,240
Finally,

117
00:08:39,840 --> 00:08:43,440
dozens of people led by the two of them

118
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:46,560
were beheaded in public.

119
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:50,080
But Yuan Feng

120
00:08:51,640 --> 00:08:57,640
and Cui Qing, who was the supervisor at the time, remained safe and sound.

121
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,720
Later,

122
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:05,520
Ye Hongru's wife paid a private visit.

123
00:09:05,880 --> 00:09:11,680
She insisted that her husband would never be involved in corruption.

124
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:15,960
To prove her husband's innocence,

125
00:09:16,040 --> 00:09:18,770
she drowned herself in the river a few days later.

126
00:09:21,160 --> 00:09:23,120
That old thief, Yuan Feng,

127
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:26,120
he is the real instigator.

128
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:31,840
All the sketches and materials for the dam

129
00:09:33,040 --> 00:09:35,960
had to be confirmed by him.

130
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:40,320
Ye Hongru and Cui Yide

131
00:09:40,440 --> 00:09:43,760
were just his scapegoats.

132
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:47,440
How is Lord Cui's relationship with Yuan Feng?

133
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,720
Cui Qing

134
00:09:50,680 --> 00:09:53,080
is Cui Yide's younger brother.

135
00:09:53,560 --> 00:09:57,800
He has no blood relation to Yuan Feng.

136
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:02,640
Cui Qing likely holds crucial evidence.

137
00:10:03,040 --> 00:10:05,520
That's why Yuan Feng won't touch him.

138
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,760
Mr. Lu.

139
00:10:19,160 --> 00:10:20,360
Mr. Lu.

140
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:24,100
The chicken soup is poisoned.

141
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,160
You poisoned it.

142
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,360
No, I didn't.

143
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:30,360
Let him go.

144
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,720
He is nothing but a pawn.

145
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:37,320
Where is Lord Cui now?

146
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:42,880
He lives in his old residence in Lantian County,

147
00:10:44,280 --> 00:10:49,000
80 li southeast of Chang'an.

148
00:10:49,280 --> 00:10:52,160
Depart immediately,

149
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:58,200
and you'll arrive by noon.

150
00:10:58,320 --> 00:10:59,480
Minister Lu.

151
00:11:02,040 --> 00:11:04,200
They will definitely go to Lu Yunxian first.

152
00:11:04,200 --> 00:11:05,600
If Lu Yunxian is not dead,

153
00:11:05,960 --> 00:11:08,200
he will definitely go to Lord Cui to find clues.

154
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:10,920
Although Minister Cui is a coward and wouldn't dare to speak out,

155
00:11:10,920 --> 00:11:11,680
as things stand now...

156
00:11:11,680 --> 00:11:12,480
No.

157
00:11:13,360 --> 00:11:14,800
We can't let them meet.

158
00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:17,160
We must ensure the secret

159
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:20,320
has no chance of leaking.

160
00:11:20,800 --> 00:11:22,440
Then I will immediately inform the yamen,

161
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:23,360
say they broke out of prison,

162
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,360
and issue a wanted poster.

163
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,800
No, no, no, no, no.

164
00:11:26,480 --> 00:11:28,560
That is the Supreme Court's job.

165
00:11:28,880 --> 00:11:32,760
What does it have to do with me, the Minister of Works?

166
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:35,210
But Minister Cui is different.

167
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:38,000
If he meets the fugitives, he will fight them.

168
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:40,250
They will mutually destroy each other

169
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:42,200
and all die.

170
00:11:42,720 --> 00:11:44,880
We can use this opportunity to catch them all,

171
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:46,200
leaving no survivors.

172
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:48,040
You've made progress.

173
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:51,120
I am tired.

174
00:12:18,360 --> 00:12:19,880
Who are you?

175
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,680
We are old friends of Elder Cui.

176
00:12:21,680 --> 00:12:23,000
We came all the way from Luoyang

177
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,160
to see him.

178
00:12:24,520 --> 00:12:25,720
Elder Cui is seriously ill.

179
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,880
He sees no one without an invitation.

180
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:29,880
Please go back.

181
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,680
I wonder if the sword in my hand

182
00:12:33,680 --> 00:12:35,520
can serve as an invitation.

183
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:15,960
How did I teach you?

184
00:13:16,160 --> 00:13:18,320
You must focus when playing chess.

185
00:13:18,680 --> 00:13:19,880
Lord Cui.

186
00:13:20,280 --> 00:13:22,610
We are here for the matter of the Anlan Dam.

187
00:13:22,640 --> 00:13:25,440
The theft of the Glazed Orb is full of suspicions.

188
00:13:25,520 --> 00:13:28,960
His Majesty ordered Dali Temple to reinvestigate the case.

189
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,680
I don't understand what you are saying.

190
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:34,160
If you are not here to play chess,

191
00:13:34,240 --> 00:13:35,700
please see the guests out.

192
00:13:57,480 --> 00:13:58,960
Who exactly are you?

193
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:01,640
I am the daughter of Li Ze,

194
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,800
the Junior Governor of Henan, Li Jinglan.

195
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:05,860
They are... So it's the daughter of Junior Governor Li.

196
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:09,880
It's said some important criminals escaped from the Luoyang prison,

197
00:14:09,960 --> 00:14:12,200
taking the Junior Governor as a hostage.

198
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:15,280
I wonder if Miss Li is a hostage

199
00:14:15,400 --> 00:14:16,840
or an accomplice.

200
00:14:16,920 --> 00:14:17,920
Cui Qing.

201
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:20,960
Now Lu Yun, Cao Shi, Ye Hongru,

202
00:14:21,040 --> 00:14:24,600
and your own brother Cui Yide are all dead.

203
00:14:25,080 --> 00:14:28,080
Moreover, Lu Yunxian was also brutally framed.

204
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:29,960
The Glazed Pearl has been recovered,

205
00:14:29,960 --> 00:14:31,760
and the Emperor is thoroughly investigating the matter.

206
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:35,640
Do you think Yuanfeng will really leave you alive?

207
00:14:42,480 --> 00:14:44,480
A few escaped convicts.

208
00:14:44,560 --> 00:14:46,720
I told you to leave earlier, but you didn't.

209
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:49,960
Now it's too late to leave.

210
00:15:07,640 --> 00:15:09,640
None of these people are pushovers.

211
00:15:10,160 --> 00:15:11,520
It seems he won't talk.

212
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:13,080
Then we'll carve a bloody path,

213
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:15,210
and pry his mouth open with our swords.

214
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:38,400
Mother.

215
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,280
Madam.

216
00:15:40,160 --> 00:15:41,960
Son.

217
00:15:49,800 --> 00:15:50,720
Go.

218
00:15:58,920 --> 00:15:59,880
Today,

219
00:15:59,960 --> 00:16:01,760
none of you are leaving.

220
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,760
Son.

221
00:16:08,400 --> 00:16:10,560
Madam.

222
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:14,800
Yuanfeng,

223
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:17,360
you untrustworthy man.

224
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,440
How could such a sinister person

225
00:16:19,560 --> 00:16:21,320
keep his word to you?

226
00:16:26,840 --> 00:16:28,360
I told you,

227
00:16:29,120 --> 00:16:31,520
he won't leave anyone alive.

228
00:16:31,960 --> 00:16:33,520
What Yuanfeng wants

229
00:16:33,640 --> 00:16:35,520
is behind that plaque.

230
00:16:46,360 --> 00:16:47,520
What is this?

231
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:49,080
Back then, Yuanfeng

232
00:16:49,320 --> 00:16:52,980
ordered my older brother to secretly alter the dam's dimensions.

233
00:16:54,760 --> 00:16:56,960
As the supervisor,

234
00:16:57,520 --> 00:17:00,120
Then proceed with the modified construction.

235
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:02,880
Most of the embezzled money

236
00:17:04,480 --> 00:17:06,760
was taken by Yuanfeng.

237
00:17:06,839 --> 00:17:10,680
My brother and I secretly divided the rest.

238
00:17:11,599 --> 00:17:13,720
After the collapse of the Anlan Dam,

239
00:17:14,079 --> 00:17:17,160
Yuanfeng summoned us privately.

240
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:20,119
He reached an agreement with Cui Yide.

241
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:22,760
My older brother would take all the blame

242
00:17:22,839 --> 00:17:25,440
to save my life.

243
00:17:25,760 --> 00:17:28,119
Falsely claiming it was the designer Ye Hongru.

244
00:17:28,119 --> 00:17:30,240
and tampered with the dam data.

245
00:17:30,600 --> 00:17:33,680
To prevent Yuan Feng from cheating,

246
00:17:33,880 --> 00:17:37,440
my older brother Cui Yide secretly kept a copy of the tampered original design draft.

247
00:17:37,440 --> 00:17:39,600
It has Yuan Feng's handwriting on it.

248
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:42,560
Yuan Feng didn't know where this draft was,

249
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,680
so he didn't dare to touch me.

250
00:17:45,480 --> 00:17:48,520
Poor Ye Hongru was loyal

251
00:17:48,600 --> 00:17:51,360
and devoted himself to the construction of the dam,

252
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:54,360
but he ended up a wronged ghost.

253
00:17:54,520 --> 00:17:59,000
They never knew where the draft was hidden.

254
00:18:00,160 --> 00:18:02,040
They never expected

255
00:18:02,640 --> 00:18:05,700
that it was actually behind the plaque in the main hall.

256
00:18:06,200 --> 00:18:11,000
Minister Lu has always had doubts about the collapse of the dam,

257
00:18:11,560 --> 00:18:17,320
so he secretly investigated the matter while transporting the disaster relief funds.

258
00:18:18,080 --> 00:18:21,960
Yuan Feng was afraid he would be exposed sooner or later,

259
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:23,880
so he came to me.

260
00:18:24,800 --> 00:18:28,360
He secretly told me the transportation route of the glazed orb.

261
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:32,720
That day, Ye Xiao ambushed on the route and robbed the orb,

262
00:18:33,040 --> 00:18:35,520
creating the illusion that the disaster relief orb disappeared.

263
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:36,840
In this way,

264
00:18:37,160 --> 00:18:41,080
Yuan Feng could impeach Lu Yunxian in the court,

265
00:18:41,920 --> 00:18:43,840
saying he was incompetent

266
00:18:44,400 --> 00:18:46,660
and stole what was entrusted to his care.

267
00:18:48,280 --> 00:18:49,920
After Yexiao got the orb,

268
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:54,130
he went to Niutou Mountain to find Cao Shi, the Deputy Magistrate of Henan.

269
00:18:54,360 --> 00:18:57,640
Cao Shi was someone I bribed.

270
00:18:58,080 --> 00:19:00,520
He killed Yexiao to silence him.

271
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:05,080
A boy climbing the mountain accidentally saw this.

272
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:07,540
The boy ran all the way down the mountain,

273
00:19:07,760 --> 00:19:09,960
but was abducted by human traffickers.

274
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:12,280
That saved me a lot of trouble.

275
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:17,920
But Cao Shi knew too much.

276
00:19:18,280 --> 00:19:21,280
So Yuanfeng had me bribe his brother Cao Fang,

277
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:23,840
to take advantage of the coffin opening in the ancient tomb

278
00:19:23,840 --> 00:19:26,560
to kill Cao Shi with venomous insects.

279
00:19:27,080 --> 00:19:28,320
You gave the Gu worm

280
00:19:29,400 --> 00:19:31,440
to Cao Fang.

281
00:19:33,600 --> 00:19:35,760
Unexpectedly, Constable Qin, who was investigating,

282
00:19:35,760 --> 00:19:37,920
refused to let the case go.

283
00:19:38,120 --> 00:19:40,000
After he secretly met Madam Cao,

284
00:19:40,080 --> 00:19:42,400
I kept following him in secret.

285
00:19:43,040 --> 00:19:45,280
Qin Rui went to Niutou Mountain

286
00:19:45,720 --> 00:19:48,760
and dug up Yexiao's body and the orb.

287
00:19:49,400 --> 00:19:51,520
He discovered my secret.

288
00:19:51,760 --> 00:19:53,720
He had to die.

289
00:20:07,040 --> 00:20:08,240
You killed my father.

290
00:20:08,320 --> 00:20:10,320
You killed my whole family.

291
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:12,920
Your family

292
00:20:14,600 --> 00:20:17,320
was killed by Yuanfeng himself.

293
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:20,400
Jueming.

294
00:20:26,320 --> 00:20:29,040
There's a secret passage behind that cabinet.

295
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:31,280
You need to leave now.

296
00:20:33,760 --> 00:20:35,220
There's no time, Jueming.

297
00:20:58,920 --> 00:20:59,800
No.

298
00:21:30,080 --> 00:21:33,740
This must be the tunnel Cui Qing prepared for fleeing to Chang'an.

299
00:21:37,000 --> 00:21:38,240
Hurry.

300
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:54,240
Hurry.

301
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:57,520
Su Lang.

302
00:21:59,880 --> 00:22:00,880
Su Lang.

303
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:02,240
Hurry up.

304
00:22:02,360 --> 00:22:04,440
Go to Chang'an quickly.

305
00:22:07,040 --> 00:22:09,880
Su Lang, what are you doing? Su Lang!

306
00:22:09,960 --> 00:22:11,360
Protect Sister Jinglan.

307
00:22:11,360 --> 00:22:13,040
If I stay, no one will be able to leave.

308
00:22:13,040 --> 00:22:13,760
Go.

309
00:22:13,840 --> 00:22:16,680
Su Lang, what are you doing? Su Lang!

310
00:22:17,560 --> 00:22:19,480
Su Lang, open the door.

311
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:31,600
Su Lang, open the door!

312
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:32,400
Su Lang,

313
00:22:32,440 --> 00:22:34,400
don't do this. Open the door!

314
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:46,560
Take the evidence to Chang'an.

315
00:22:46,720 --> 00:22:48,080
Go!

316
00:24:10,280 --> 00:24:11,520
Su Lang.

317
00:24:16,320 --> 00:24:17,920
I'll wait for your return.

318
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:23,480
You must come back.

319
00:26:21,760 --> 00:26:24,680
Come, let's pray together, okay?

320
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:26,280
Okay.

321
00:27:12,000 --> 00:27:13,360
I'm back.

322
00:27:18,000 --> 00:27:19,320
Son.

323
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:27,600
Ah.

324
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:44,560
Giddy-up.

325
00:28:53,240 --> 00:28:57,080
Yuan Feng, the Minister of Works, took bribes and bent the law,

326
00:28:57,160 --> 00:28:59,960
colluded with others using his position,

327
00:29:00,040 --> 00:29:01,700
and disregarded human lives.

328
00:29:01,960 --> 00:29:04,040
He is sentenced to beheading.

329
00:29:04,440 --> 00:29:08,300
All his embezzled wealth shall be confiscated to the state treasury.

330
00:29:14,120 --> 00:29:15,680
I heard you wanted to see me.

331
00:29:22,200 --> 00:29:23,600
Who are you?

332
00:29:23,760 --> 00:29:26,880
Why do you keep coming after me?

333
00:29:26,960 --> 00:29:28,240
Who am I?

334
00:29:28,360 --> 00:29:30,640
I am the one who will tear you to pieces,

335
00:29:30,880 --> 00:29:32,540
personally throw you in jail,

336
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,840
and watch you die.

337
00:29:36,040 --> 00:29:39,160
The tens of thousands of people from Dongshui Town who suffered from the dam collapse

338
00:29:39,160 --> 00:29:40,920
all died because of you.

339
00:29:42,520 --> 00:29:45,560
You killed my father, my mother,

340
00:29:46,880 --> 00:29:48,940
as well as my sister and grandfather.

341
00:29:50,560 --> 00:29:53,560
People like you deserve to die.

342
00:29:54,480 --> 00:29:57,520
You are an orphan from Dongshui Town.

343
00:29:59,280 --> 00:30:03,000
I will never forget the look in my mother's eyes when she died,

344
00:30:03,200 --> 00:30:05,560
along with my sister and grandfather.

345
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:07,440
It was you

346
00:30:08,320 --> 00:30:10,000
who destroyed my home.

347
00:30:10,080 --> 00:30:11,360
It was you

348
00:30:11,680 --> 00:30:13,600
who took everything from me.

349
00:30:14,520 --> 00:30:17,080
I am the ant you spoke of.

350
00:30:20,040 --> 00:30:21,600
Do you remember now?

351
00:30:23,680 --> 00:30:24,480
Five people in total.

352
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:26,680
Two children and two adults, all accounted for.

353
00:30:26,680 --> 00:30:27,600
Once this fire burns,

354
00:30:27,600 --> 00:30:29,330
there will be no evidence left.

355
00:30:31,880 --> 00:30:33,800
A bunch of ants

356
00:30:34,640 --> 00:30:37,040
trying to shake an elephant.

357
00:30:37,680 --> 00:30:39,000
How ridiculous.

358
00:30:39,560 --> 00:30:40,800
How laughable.

359
00:30:41,920 --> 00:30:43,760
My name is Qin Nian.

360
00:30:44,760 --> 00:30:46,520
I am a descendant of the Qin family,

361
00:30:46,520 --> 00:30:48,080
the son of Qin Rui.

362
00:30:48,360 --> 00:30:49,090
Impossible.

363
00:30:49,120 --> 00:30:50,120
Remember?

364
00:30:50,280 --> 00:30:52,240
Impossible.

365
00:30:54,640 --> 00:30:56,440
Look at you now.

366
00:30:58,240 --> 00:31:01,840
You spent decades scheming,

367
00:31:01,920 --> 00:31:03,840
only to become a prisoner.

368
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:06,320
People like you

369
00:31:06,720 --> 00:31:09,440
will be cursed for generations.

370
00:31:11,400 --> 00:31:12,560
You lied to me.

371
00:31:12,640 --> 00:31:16,080
You lied to me. You lied to me!

372
00:31:22,160 --> 00:31:24,200
I will watch you die.

373
00:31:27,520 --> 00:31:29,960
I will watch you die.

374
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,160
Impossible.

375
00:31:38,760 --> 00:31:40,240
Impossible.

376
00:31:40,720 --> 00:31:42,520
Ants.

377
00:31:44,320 --> 00:31:46,600
They are all ants.

378
00:31:56,160 --> 00:31:59,320
I will watch you die.

379
00:32:06,600 --> 00:32:10,280
Under the imperial edict, Buliangren Jue Ming,

380
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:13,680
in the investigation of the Glazed Pearl case,

381
00:32:13,760 --> 00:32:16,360
has finally retrieved the national treasure.

382
00:32:16,440 --> 00:32:18,400
With outstanding merits,

383
00:32:18,760 --> 00:32:22,360
he is hereby appointed Minister of Dali Temple.

384
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:25,240
May he uphold justice

385
00:32:25,360 --> 00:32:29,880
and enforce the law. Execute as ordered.

386
00:32:32,280 --> 00:32:34,720
The Emperor ordered you to take office at Dali Temple immediately.

387
00:32:34,720 --> 00:32:37,180
That is a high position many people dream of.

388
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:39,300
Why are you delaying your departure?

389
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:41,160
I still have one thing left unfinished.

390
00:32:41,160 --> 00:32:42,440
What is it?

391
00:32:43,280 --> 00:32:45,810
I only survived by using Jue Ming's identity.

392
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:47,360
But I still don't know

393
00:32:47,480 --> 00:32:50,480
why his mother, Shen Zhiling, died.

394
00:32:51,120 --> 00:32:52,760
I remember my grandfather saying

395
00:32:52,760 --> 00:32:54,490
she was stabbed several times,

396
00:32:54,920 --> 00:32:56,480
and every cut was fatal.

397
00:32:56,840 --> 00:32:58,400
The crime scene was a pharmacy,

398
00:32:58,400 --> 00:33:00,880
but there weren't many medicinal herbs in the house.

399
00:33:00,880 --> 00:33:03,940
So my grandfather suspected she had another identity.

400
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:06,600
The only clue to this case

401
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:08,400
is the murder weapon.

402
00:33:09,040 --> 00:33:12,300
That sword with the blue dragon and roaring tiger pattern.

403
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:18,480
For the name Jueming,

404
00:33:18,560 --> 00:33:20,120
I will solve this case.

405
00:33:25,800 --> 00:33:27,640
I'll go with you.

